4  5
5  6
6  7

query II nosort
FETCH FORWARD 3 foo
----
7  8
8  9
9  10

query II
FETCH RELATIVE 3 foo
----
12  13

query II
FETCH FORWARD foo
----
13  14

query II
FETCH ABSOLUTE 13 foo
----
13  14

query II
